A transport-tech company, with a focus on training, verifying, and outsourcing the best drivers to individuals and organisations, Drivers NG engages in recruiting, vetting, and training drivers to meet a variety of needs that clients may have such as corporate drivers, personal drivers, sales van drivers, truck drivers, drivers for Uber, etc. The company envisions using its platform to assist employers in utilising the services of professionally trained and verified drivers to achieve their business objectives. You can get a driver for a day, a week, a weekend, a month or on a full-time basis and the driver will be at your service within 24 hours of the request. Drivers undergo periodic medical tests (every six months) to ascertain their physical and mental health to ensure they are fit for the job.